<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 00:58:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>耶伦：新兴市场对中国工厂产能过剩表示担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/yellen-emerging-markets-share-concerns-chinas-excess-factory-capacity-2024-07-26/</link><description>美国财长耶伦周五表示，包括一些G20国家在内的新兴市场与她一样对中国工业产能过剩感到担忧，并应敦促北京改变其经济模式。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 23:29:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/yellen-emerging-markets-share-concerns-chinas-excess-factory-capacity-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>上海推出138亿美元基金支持集成电路、生物医药、人工智能等领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-launches-138-bln-funds-boost-integrated-circuit-biomedicine-ai-sectors-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国商业中心上海周五宣布提供 1000 亿元人民币（137.9 亿美元）的资金，以促进其集成电路、生物医药和人工智能 (AI) 产业的发展。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 13:36:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-launches-138-bln-funds-boost-integrated-circuit-biomedicine-ai-sectors-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>英国敦促中国阻止其公司支持俄罗斯军事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-urges-china-prevent-its-companies-supporting-russias-military-2024-07-26/</link><description>英国外交大臣戴维·拉米 (David Lammy) 与中国外长王毅会面后，其办公室周五表示，英国外交大臣戴维·拉米 (David Lammy) 敦促中国阻止其公司支持俄罗斯军队。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 09:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-urges-china-prevent-its-companies-supporting-russias-military-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国外长表示中韩应避免外部干涉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-skorea-should-avoid-external-interference-chinese-foreign-minister-says-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周五对韩国外长表示，中韩应避免外部因素干扰，扩大共同利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 09:17:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-skorea-should-avoid-external-interference-chinese-foreign-minister-says-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国进口伊朗原油在东北找到新市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-iranian-crude-imports-find-new-market-northeast-2024-07-26/</link><description>油轮追踪公司和贸易消息人士称，自去年年底以来，进口的伊朗原油一直流入港口和炼油城市大连，帮助该国的石油购买量维持在接近历史最高水平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 07:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-iranian-crude-imports-find-new-market-northeast-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国称中日关系处于“关键阶段”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-foreign-minister-says-relations-with-japan-critical-stage-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国外长王毅周五对日本外长表示，中日关系正处于关键阶段，双方讨论了包括在中国被拘留的日本公民、食品进口禁令和半导体限制等棘手问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 07:55:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-foreign-minister-says-relations-with-japan-critical-stage-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国通过消费刺激措施走出了一条不走寻常路的路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/fridges-not-bridges-china-veers-off-beaten-path-with-consumer-stimulus-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国利用超长期国债为消费品以旧换新计划提供资金，这背离了通常通过增加投资来支持经济的做法，并引发了人们对针对家庭需求采取更多刺激措施的预期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 05:57:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/fridges-not-bridges-china-veers-off-beaten-path-with-consumer-stimulus-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国企业寻求削减印尼新建镍冶炼厂的股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-firms-seek-cut-stakes-new-indonesian-nickel-smelters-2024-07-26/</link><description>一位印度尼西亚官员周五表示，中国公司正在与潜在投资者进行谈判，以减少其在印度尼西亚镍冶炼厂的股份，以使其产品有资格获得美国电动汽车税收抵免。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 05:50:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-firms-seek-cut-stakes-new-indonesian-nickel-smelters-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>台风“嘉美”袭击台湾和菲律宾后袭击中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/typhoon-gaemi-lashes-southeast-china-after-pounding-taiwan-flooding-philippines-2024-07-26/</link><description>周五，台风“盖美”给中国沿海福建省的城镇带来大雨和强风，这是今年袭击中国的最强风暴，开始向人口稠密的内陆地区移动，受到广泛关注。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 05:44:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/typhoon-gaemi-lashes-southeast-china-after-pounding-taiwan-flooding-philippines-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国降息序列暗示MLF作用减弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rate-cuts-sequence-hints-reduced-role-mlf-2024-07-26/</link><description>分析师表示，中国最新的一系列降息表明央行的货币框架已经发生变化，短期回购利率成为主要信号，中期借贷便利（MLF）的作用减弱。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 05:09:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rate-cuts-sequence-hints-reduced-role-mlf-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部长王毅承诺与俄罗斯共同致力于东亚和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-foreign-minister-wang-pledges-work-with-russia-east-asian-peace-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国外长王毅表示，在国际动荡中，中俄应就东亚合作保持沟通协调，促进地区和平稳定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 02:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-foreign-minister-wang-pledges-work-with-russia-east-asian-peace-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>美军寻求战略优势，在中国紧张局势中建立澳大利亚北部基地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-seeking-strategic-advantages-builds-up-australias-northern-bases-2024-07-26/</link><description>路透社对文件的审查以及对美国和澳大利亚国防官员的采访显示，美国军方正在澳大利亚北部建设基础设施，以帮助其在与中国爆发危机时向南海投射力量。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 01:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-seeking-strategic-advantages-builds-up-australias-northern-bases-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>王毅：中印应相向而行，关系具有重要影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-india-should-work-same-direction-relations-have-an-important-impact-says-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅表示，希望中印双方相向而行，探讨周边国家相处之道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 23:48:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-india-should-work-same-direction-relations-have-an-important-impact-says-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>印度和中国同意紧急处理边界问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-china-agree-approach-border-issues-with-urgency-2024-07-25/</link><description>印度外交部长苏杰生周四在老挝会见了中国外长王毅，两国领导人同意尽快解决边界问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:32:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-china-agree-approach-border-issues-with-urgency-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰要求香港不要让俄罗斯规避制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraine-asks-hong-kong-not-let-russia-circumvent-sanctions-2024-07-25/</link><description>乌克兰外交部长德米特罗·库莱巴周四访问香港，并呼吁其领导人李约翰阻止俄罗斯利用香港作为规避西方因莫斯科全面乌克兰战争而对其实施制裁的手段。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 13:23:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraine-asks-hong-kong-not-let-russia-circumvent-sanctions-2024-07-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>